#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Appointments App</b>:</strong> Let families book meetings to "
"discuss camp options easily, reducing no-shows with automatic "
"reminders.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບ ນັດໝາຍ (Appointments App)</b>:</strong> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຄອບຄົວຈອງເວລາພົບປະເພື່"
"ອສົນທະນາກ່ຽວກັບທາງເລືອກຂອງຄ້າຍໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ, ຫຼຸດຜ່ອນການຜິດນັດດ້ວຍລະບົບເຕືອນອັດຕະໂນມັດ.<br/>"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong><b>CRM App</b>: </strong>Capture inquiries from your website, "
"qualify leads in a visual pipeline, and convert interest into confirmed "
"bookings.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບ CRM</b>: </strong>ເກັບກຳຂໍ້ມູນການສອບຖາມຈາກເວັບໄຊທ໌, ຄັດກອງລູກຄ້າທີ່ມຸ່ງຫວັງໃ"
"ນລະບົບ pipeline, ແລະ ປ່ຽນຄວາມສົນໃຈໃຫ້ກາຍເປັນການຈອງທີ່ຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ.<br/>"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Events App</b>: </strong>Create and manage every camp session "
"with custom forms, capacity tracking, and automated emails to keep parents "
"informed.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບ ເຫດການ (Events App)</b>: </strong>ສ້າງ ແລະ ຈັດການແຕ່ລະຮອບຄ້າຍດ້ວຍແບ"
"ບຟອມທີ່ກຳນົດເອງ, ຕິດຕາມຈຳນວນທີ່ຮອງຮັບໄດ້, ແລະ ສົ່ງອີເມລອັດຕະໂນມັດເພື່ອແຈ້ງໃຫ້ພໍ່ແມ່ຊາບ.<br/>"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Projects App</b>: </strong>Organize the behind-the-scenes "
"logistics using task lists and deadlines to ensure every activity is "
"prepared to perfection.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບ ໂຄງການ (Projects App)</b>: </strong>ຈັດລະບຽບວຽກງານເບື້ອງຫຼັງໂດຍໃຊ້ລາ"
"ຍການວຽກ ແລະ ກຳນົດເວລາ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ໝັ້ນໃຈວ່າທຸກກິດຈະກຳຖືກກະກຽມຢ່າງສົມບູນແບບ.<br/>"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Sign App</b>: </strong>Collect parental consent securely with "
"reusable digital signature templates, ensuring all legal documents are "
"signed and stored centrally.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບ ເຊັນ (Sign App)</b>: </strong>ເກັບກຳການຍິນຍອມຈາກພໍ່ແມ່ຢ່າງປອດໄພດ້ວຍແມ່ແ"
"ບບລາຍເຊັນດິຈິຕອນທີ່ໃຊ້ຊ້ຳໄດ້, ເພື່ອໃຫ້ໝັ້ນໃຈວ່າເອກະສານທາງກົດໝາຍທັງໝົດຖືກເຊັນ ແລະ ຈັດເກັບໄວ້ຢູ່ບ່ອນດຽ"
"ວ.<br/>"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Website App</b>: </strong>Showcase your camps online with mobile-"
"friendly pages, integrated registration, and secure payment processing to "
"boost enrollments.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>ແອັບ ເວັບໄຊທ໌ (Website App)</b>: </strong>ສະແດງຄ້າຍຂອງທ່ານໃນຮູບແບບອອນລາຍ"
"ດ້ວຍໜ້າເວັບທີ່ຮອງຮັບມືຖື, ລະບົບລົງທະບຽນໃນຕົວ, ແລະ ການຊຳລະເງິນທີ່ປອດໄພ ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຍອດການລົງທະບຽ"
"ນ.<br/>"

